turned back  and faced the maximal bot again.  "Please tell me where 
I may hunt."  She then looked down with a frown.  "I'm sorry, please 
forgive me.  I forgot in all the fighting.  My name is SnowCat.  What 
is your name, and thank you for helping against the other bot over 
there."
